text: Raúl Machacuay (born 18 February 1983) is a Peruvian long distance runner who specialises in the marathon. He competed in the men's marathon event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Peruvian male long-distance runners Category:Peruvian male marathon runners Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Peru
